    <item>
      <title>格陵兰总理称已准备好与特朗普合作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/greenland-is-ready-to-cooperate-with-trump-prime-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格陵兰总理表示，他将寻求与美国建立更紧密的关系，凸显了在唐纳德·特朗普重新引起关注的背景下，北极岛国正在推动独立。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/greenland-is-ready-to-cooperate-with-trump-prime-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 20:52:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>洛克菲勒的张先生：10 年期收益率是“尾巴摇狗”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/10-year-yield-is-tail-wagging-dog-rockefeller-s-chang-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[洛克菲勒全球家族办公室首席投资官 Jimmy Chang 表示，10 年期美国国债收益率是“目前最令人担忧的因素”。Chang 在接受“彭博收盘”采访时还表示，他看到了并购市场的势头，并讨论了他对盈利增长的展望。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/10-year-yield-is-tail-wagging-dog-rockefeller-s-chang-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 20:36:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱迪生国际公司因火灾诉讼案而债务大幅下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/edison-international-s-bonds-extend-drop-as-la-wildfires-rage-on</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱迪生国际公司 (Edison International) 的债券周一相对于美国国债走弱，延续了一周的跌势，此前该公司遭到诉讼，指控其设备引发了洛杉矶周边的一场山火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/edison-international-s-bonds-extend-drop-as-la-wildfires-rage-on</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 18:50:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克利夫兰克利夫斯和纽柯考虑联合竞购美国钢铁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/cleveland-cliffs-and-nucor-said-to-consider-joint-us-steel-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，克利夫兰-克利夫斯公司正与纽柯公司合作，考虑联合竞购美国钢铁公司。克利夫兰-克利夫斯公司的高层后来在新闻发布会上证实了他对这家美国钢铁制造商的兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/cleveland-cliffs-and-nucor-said-to-consider-joint-us-steel-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 18:31:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普上台后，华尔街预计美元涨势将扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/wall-street-sees-dollar-rallying-further-as-trump-enters-stage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国经济复苏、降息预期减弱，以及新任总统唐纳德·特朗普誓言实施严厉关税，华尔街预测美元将进一步上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/wall-street-sees-dollar-rallying-further-as-trump-enters-stage</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 18:16:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业数据公布后，美国国债抛售引发全球市场恐慌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/treasuries-selloff-ripples-through-world-markets-after-jobs-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五强劲的就业报告增强了人们对美联储将在今年几乎全年暂停降息的猜测，美国国债延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/treasuries-selloff-ripples-through-world-markets-after-jobs-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 10:46:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于美国对俄罗斯的制裁威胁供应，油价创下五个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国对俄罗斯能源行业实施新一轮制裁，威胁到全球最大产油国之一的石油供应，油价收于每桶 79 美元附近，创下五个月新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 23:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
